    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Joy
---
Even if you put all the pleasures of the entire world together in one great
heap, they say that the ultimate bliss that each individual soul is
destined to attain, even one little portion of that bliss, far outweighs
the total pleasure that this world is capable of giving.
